<br>
I rarely have many buffs, so I placed my window at the top of my screen.  I removed the window borders so that the majority of the screen would be visible.  The only problem that I had was that in a raid I wouldn't know when I was close to 15 buffs.<br>
<br>
I tried to add text to each buff with 1), 2), etc but they showed up when there were no buffs.<br>
<br>
My solution:  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> I changed the text color of buff slots 11-14 to yellow, and the text for buff 15 to red.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  Now at a glance I can tell how many buffs I have.<br>
<br>
It is a very simple change, so I won't bother trying to find a place to host the change or anything.  if someone needs help, post here and I will answer their questions.<br>
